* Dinobot knew the answer to Tavatron's question but wasn't sure if he 
should answer, didn't she know that he was originally a Predacon?
He snarled, she had answered his question so it was his turn to answer hers. 
It was only fair.*

" No. I was not always a Maximal."

*Dinobot growled.*

" I grew up as a Predacon. I left the Predacons soon after I helped steal 
the Golden Disc from Cybertron and crashed on earth. I joined Optimus Primal 
and have been a Maximal ever since."

* There, he had answered her question. He hoped that he had given a 
satisfactory answer but she was free to ask any other questions if she 
wished.*
